    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，我梳理一下：Client发HTTPS GET到LoadBalancer，LoadBalancer转HTTP给NGINX，这里要标注HealthTech_EMR_Sync对吧？然后NGINX内部有个路由循环，再转发到Webservice。返回路径上，Webservice→NGINX带LabAnalyzer标识，NGINX→LoadBalancer带PatientRecords，最后LoadBalancer→Client带HIPAA_Vault。这样理解对吗？",
